\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp data-wp-block=\"{\u0026#34;dropCap\u0026#34;:false}\" data-wp-block-name=\"core/paragraph\"\u003eAt the time, then-Stellantis CEO Carlos Tavares called the Amazon partnership “an integral part of our capability building roadmap,” adding that Amazon’s tech prowess would help transform the driving experience of its vehicles. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp data-wp-block=\"{\u0026#34;dropCap\u0026#34;:false}\" data-wp-block-name=\"core/paragraph\"\u003e“By leveraging artificial intelligence and cloud solutions, we will transform our vehicles into personalized living spaces and enhance the overall customer experience, making our vehicles the most wanted, most captivating place to be, even when not driving,” Tavares said.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003csection\u003e\u003carticle\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca aria-label=\"View post: 10 Best 0% APR Car Deals in June 2025\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"https://www.autoblog.com/carbuying/10-best-0-apr-car-deals-june-2025\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Ford F-150 Lightning Lariat\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(min-width: 790px) 375px, (min-width: 768px) calc(50vw - 24px), calc(100vw - 24px)\" srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_16,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEwNDk1NjA0OTUzMzI3NDQx/f-150-lightning_lariat_off-road_04.jpg 16w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_32,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEwNDk1NjA0OTUzMzI3NDQx/f-150-lightning_lariat_off-road_04.jpg 32w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_48,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEwNDk1NjA0OTUzMzI3NDQx/f-150-lightning_lariat_off-road_04.jpg 48w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_64,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEwNDk1NjA0OTUzMzI3NDQx/f-150-lightning_lariat_off-road_04.jpg 64w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_96,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEwNDk1NjA0OTUzMzI3NDQx/f-150-lightning_lariat_off-road_04.jpg 96w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_128,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEwNDk1NjA0OTUzMzI3NDQx/f-150-lightning_lariat_off-road_04.jpg 128w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_256,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEwNDk1NjA0OTUzMzI3NDQx/f-150-lightning_lariat_off-road_04.jpg 256w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_384,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEwNDk1NjA0OTUzMzI3NDQx/f-150-lightning_lariat_off-road_04.jpg 384w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_640,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEwNDk1NjA0OTUzMzI3NDQx/f-150-lightning_lariat_off-road_04.jpg 640w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_750,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEwNDk1NjA0OTUzMzI3NDQx/f-150-lightning_lariat_off-road_04.jpg 750w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_828,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEwNDk1NjA0OTUzMzI3NDQx/f-150-lightning_lariat_off-road_04.jpg 828w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1080,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEwNDk1NjA0OTUzMzI3NDQx/f-150-lightning_lariat_off-road_04.jpg 1080w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1200,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEwNDk1NjA0OTUzMzI3NDQx/f-150-lightning_lariat_off-road_04.jpg 1200w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1920,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEwNDk1NjA0OTUzMzI3NDQx/f-150-lightning_lariat_off-road_04.jpg 1920w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_2048,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEwNDk1NjA0OTUzMzI3NDQx/f-150-lightning_lariat_off-road_04.jpg 2048w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_3840,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEwNDk1NjA0OTUzMzI3NDQx/f-150-lightning_lariat_off-road_04.jpg 3840w\" src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_3840,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEwNDk1NjA0OTUzMzI3NDQx/f-150-lightning_lariat_off-road_04.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/article\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"final-thoughts\"\u003eFinal thoughts\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp data-wp-block=\"{\u0026#34;dropCap\u0026#34;:false}\" data-wp-block-name=\"core/paragraph\"\u003eThe end of this partnership comes as Stellantis enters a transition period following the tenure of Carlos Tavares, with the newly appointed CEO, Antonio Filosa, taking the helm in June. I think that the rather quiet realization of the end of this partnership goes to show that Stellantis is prioritizing its approach going forward.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp data-wp-block=\"{\u0026#34;dropCap\u0026#34;:false}\" data-wp-block-name=\"core/paragraph\"\u003eThat being said, the fact that we are in the era of the software-defined vehicle is rather interesting, especially considering that companies like Google (with Google Built-in) and Apple’s CarPlay Ultra are making their way to dominate every screen on dashboards. If it came to light, having Amazon in the mix would have been a very left-field option. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003csection\u003e\u003carticle\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca aria-label=\"View post: 2025 Lexus LX 700h: Is It Worth \u0026amp;#x24;115,350? My In-Depth Guide to Its Upsides \u0026amp;amp;amp; Downsides\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"https://www.autoblog.com/carbuying/2025-lexus-lx-700h-is-it-worth-115350\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"2025 Lexus LX 700h Ultra Luxury\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(min-width: 790px) 375px, (min-width: 768px) calc(50vw - 24px), calc(100vw - 24px)\" srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_16,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEyNjU4NTYwOTUyMjQ3ODE3/2025-lexus-lx-700h-ultra-luxury.jpg 16w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_32,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEyNjU4NTYwOTUyMjQ3ODE3/2025-lexus-lx-700h-ultra-luxury.jpg 32w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_48,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEyNjU4NTYwOTUyMjQ3ODE3/2025-lexus-lx-700h-ultra-luxury.jpg 48w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_64,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEyNjU4NTYwOTUyMjQ3ODE3/2025-lexus-lx-700h-ultra-luxury.jpg 64w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_96,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEyNjU4NTYwOTUyMjQ3ODE3/2025-lexus-lx-700h-ultra-luxury.jpg 96w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_128,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEyNjU4NTYwOTUyMjQ3ODE3/2025-lexus-lx-700h-ultra-luxury.jpg 128w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_256,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEyNjU4NTYwOTUyMjQ3ODE3/2025-lexus-lx-700h-ultra-luxury.jpg 256w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_384,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEyNjU4NTYwOTUyMjQ3ODE3/2025-lexus-lx-700h-ultra-luxury.jpg 384w, https://www.aut